cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a novel framework for skin lesion segmentation using deep learning techniques. The proposed method involves feature learning and decision fusion, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) research. The use of dermoscopic images also suggests a potential connection to medical imaging (cs.MM) research. Finally, the paper involves analysis of decision consistency, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
